          <span class="eyebrow text-[9px] text-[#7d8696]">Organization&nbsp;Transport&nbsp;Protocol</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[13px] mt-3 leading-[1.6] text-[#8893a4]">
          The operating platform where your people and AI agents run as one team. One chart, one scoreboard, one weekly meeting.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-12 text-sm">
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#7d8696] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Platform</div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-[13px]">
            <a href="/browse" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Browse</a>
            <a href="/graph" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Graph</a>
            <a href="/pricing" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Pricing</a>
            <a href="/publish" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Publish</a>
            <a href="/protocol" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Protocol</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#7d8696] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Learn</div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-[13px]">
            <a href="/glossary" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Glossary</a>
            <a href="/faq" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">FAQ</a>
            <a href="/answers" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Answers</a>
            <a href="/guide" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Guide</a>
            <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Blog</a>
            <a href="/mcp" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">MCP Hub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#7d8696] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Company</div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-[13px]">
            <a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">About</a>
            <a href="/partners" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Partners</a>
            <a href="/whats-new" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">What's New</a>
            <a href="/investors" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Investors</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[10px] text-[#5f6878] mt-10 leading-[1.6] max-w-2xl">
      OTP is an independent platform. Best practices in the library are sourced from publicly available content and attributed to their original authors. OTP is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by any third-party organizations referenced.
